{"tid":61254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奇聞】金髮加粗眉 　山西一商場驚現「特朗普雞」迎新年","createTime":"2016-12-31T06:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T09:05:57.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"375f24c4fe762e5da8cf32887c95b803fe0192ac","tid":61254,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m1.ablwang.com/uploadfile/2016/1229/20161229111926716.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.ablwang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2016%2F1229%2F20161229111926716.png&h=cbfc6df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.ablwang.com/uploadfile/2016/1229/20161229111926425.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.ablwang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2016%2F1229%2F20161229111926425.png&h=97c9edd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法廣DR網絡圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12月28日本周三，隨着新年的臨近中國大陸山西省的一家購物商場外，樹立起了一隻形似特朗普，留着其標誌性&ldquo;頭髮搭橋&rdquo;髮型的巨型卡通雞雕塑，寓意新年化身特朗普，準備預祝雞年的到來。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這一以特朗普長相為藍圖建造的&ldquo;特朗普雞&rdquo;雕塑，在本周早些時候被放入該購物商場的入口之外，供遊人觀賞。<br />\n<br />\n該雕塑除了具有特朗普經典的金橘色&ldquo;頭髮搭橋&rdquo;髮型，神似其本人演講時的雙眉上翹，嘴巴大張的神態，更有意思的是&ldquo;特朗普&rdquo;雞的雕塑雙翅，還分別做出了&ldquo;OK&rdquo;和指向遠方的手勢，頗有特朗普講話時的風範。而該雕塑在當地一經推出，便立即引來了附近購物者和遊客的圍觀和拍照。<br />\n<br />\n儘管作為總統候選人的特朗普曾威脅一旦上台，要對中國商品實施高額關稅，並質控大陸政府為&ldquo;彙率操縱國&rdquo;。但就如曾經奧巴馬當選總統時，在中國大賣的&ldquo;奧巴馬&rdquo;T恤一樣，此次迎新年&ldquo;特朗普雞&rdquo;的推出，也未嘗不可以看作是其本人在中國民間是否受歡迎的風向標之一。"},{"pid":"5f3a93444cc48317940155eda96669c28208f515","tid":61254,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e8e74b000728a1df0a803a0e862a4ffc0711ea","tid":61254,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"唔知侵侵見到會有咩反應呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a7e6116795068392e3311bc66be386bab09e76","tid":61254,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e67f933fa559f3e5b78421776a016fc46d493be6","tid":61254,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042ea39dbf1619eff05c82e79be6705575d497f9","tid":61254,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"個樣又幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca522bc95acc1766e8e1846ddc3e673eb9905ea1","tid":61254,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"今次靚抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0391ccf6c58835c9a189116942df42a3b284dcf7","tid":61254,"uid":20178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"張相好似好假"},{"pid":"e3f4d099d487e2d1c64239fd8c8f4a31ce410c8d","tid":61254,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"中國今次終於有原創野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚得意"},{"pid":"efe9731bd39f1e643c0646c485e8cfad8e3acbdb","tid":61254,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f195b311